"Another set is currently uploading" = "另一个集合正在上传";
"Backup runs automatically when the app is closed. Includes all your sets and images." = "应用关闭时自动运行备份。包含所有集合和图片。";
"Camera activates silently in background when Performance opens. Vibrates once on recognition." = "表演开始时相机静默激活。识别到文字时振动一次。";
"Camera starts silently when Performance opens. Recognized text auto-reveals: letters → word set, digits → number set." = "表演开始时相机静默启动。识别到的文字自动揭示：字母→单词集合，数字→数字集合。";
"Deflates the searched profile, then inflates yours when you press the volume button." = "缩小搜索的个人资料，然后在按音量键时放大您自己的资料。";
"Fetch text from Inject or Custom API when Performance opens" = "表演开始时从Inject或自定义API获取文字";
"Fetches a word/text from 11z.co using your Inject ID." = "使用您的Inject ID从11z.co获取单词/文字。";
"Masks what you type in Explore so spectators see a different word. Pressing SPACE triggers the word reveal." = "隐藏您在探索中输入的内容，让观众看到不同的词。按空格键触发揭示。";
"Text fetched automatically when Performance opens" = "表演开始时自动获取文字";
"Another app sends the image as base64. Vault handles resize and compression automatically." = "另一个应用以Base64格式发送图片。Vault自动处理大小调整和压缩。";
"Open this URL to trigger a reveal directly when Performance opens" = "表演开始时打开此URL直接触发揭示";
"Use these URLs in iOS Shortcuts to update your profile picture automatically when Performance opens." = "在iOS快捷指令中使用这些URL，在表演开始时自动更新个人资料图片。";
"Upload a screenshot of your iPhone home screen showing the Instagram icon." = "上传显示Instagram图标的iPhone主屏幕截图。";
"Enable fake home screen" = "启用虚假主屏幕";
"Pre-select a post from any profile. During performance, the spectator scrolls through their posts and the scroll always stops on the forced image." = "从任意个人资料预选一个帖子。表演时，观众滚动帖子，滚动总会停在强制图片上。";
"Pre-select a reel from any profile. In Performance, swipe the grid to set a position, then open Explore — the reel will appear at that exact slot." = "从任意个人资料预选一个Reel。在表演中，滑动网格设置位置，然后打开探索——Reel将出现在该位置。";
"Instantly unarchive and reveal photos" = "立即取消归档并揭示照片";
"Unarchive photos from the active set to reveal a word or number. Choose one or more input methods below." = "从活跃集合取消归档照片以揭示单词或数字。选择以下一种或多种输入方式。";
"Swipe left or right on the photo grid to build a number. Tap the Posts icon to unarchive the matching photo from the active number set." = "在照片网格上向左或向右滑动以构建数字。点击帖子图标从活跃数字集合取消归档匹配照片。";
"Swipe the grid to secretly build a number (1–100), then open Explore. When you visit an audience member's profile the selected counter appears inflated. Press a volume button to start the countdown back to the real number." = "秘密滑动网格构建数字(1-100)，然后打开探索。访问观众个人资料时，选定的计数器会显示为膨胀。按音量键开始倒计时回到真实数字。";
"Register an even number of spectators. The app splits them in half automatically: first half → 📅 date (their followers), second half → 🕐 time (their following)." = "注册偶数个观众。应用自动将其分为两半：前半 → 📅 日期（他们的粉丝），后半 → 🕐 时间（他们的关注）。";
"Register an even number of spectators. The app splits them in half: first half → 📅 date, second half → 🕐 time. Both Auto and Dual use the **same math** — the only difference is *who does the work*." = "注册偶数个观众。应用将其分为两半：前半 → 📅 日期，后半 → 🕐 时间。Auto和Dual使用**相同的数学**——唯一区别是*谁来做工作*。";
"The app silently fetches your latest followers via the Instagram API. It reads two numbers from each person's profile:" = "应用通过Instagram API静默获取您的最新粉丝。从每个人的个人资料读取两个数字：";
"The first half of captured spectators form the date group. The second half form the time group. Each Explore post then shows forced numbers: **followers = today's date + sum(date group's follower counts)**, **following = current time + sum(time group's following counts)**." = "捕获的观众前半部分构成日期组，后半部分构成时间组。探索帖子显示强制数字：**粉丝 = 今日日期 + 日期组粉丝总数**，**关注 = 当前时间 + 时间组关注总数**。";
